{"type":"message","id":"676dcfd2","parentId":"448f28eb","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:55:56.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the music API is returning empty because there's no track playing. The Music app shows paused state. That's expected - when nothing is playing, it returns empty. The API itself is working fine.\n\nLet me also check if there are any obvious issues with the data persistence. Let me try adding an entry to habits to see if it saves.\n\nActually, let me test the Money widget - I'll add an entry and see if it persists.\n","thinkingSignature":"3ecd7f8b3827ba21c2431c528437138872ea05067c2208816b9625ce3be92756"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pn0p5312ogb7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test money API with POST\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3001/api/money/action \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"action\":\"add\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"test123\",\"date\":\"May 3, 2026\",\"description\":\"Test entry\",\"amount\":-25.50,\"type\":\"expense\"}}' 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":191,"output":193,"cacheRead":76032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76416,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777787749937,"responseId":"06461666e379a2437e69459e2d765f6b"}}
