{"type":"message","id":"83c5b230","parentId":"fa4c9054","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:56:35.031Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full architecture. Let me verify all the widgets are working by checking the API endpoints and then test the live site. The main issues could be:\n\n1. The frontend may not have proper CORS for the API calls to localhost:3001\n2. The music widget needs Apple Music app running to get track info\n3. The email widget depends on gog being configured\n\nBut looking at the Vite config, the `/api` requests proxy to `http://localhost:3001` - so in production (served from port 8787), the API calls should work through the proxy.\n\nWait - the vite proxy only works in dev mode. When serving the built dist files, vite proxy doesn't apply. \n\nSo the built app has hardcoded API calls to `/api/*`. The server.cjs only proxies `/tools` to the gateway - it doesn't proxy `/api` to localhost:3001. This is the bug. When the built app calls `/api/emails` from port 8787, the server can't find that route, so it falls back to index.html for the SPA, which means the API calls actually go nowhere.\n\nBut since the site is working and I can see real email data, either the app is being served from port 3001 directly, or there's a proxy setup I'm missing. Looking at the lsof output showing the API is responding on localhost:3001 with actual email data, Bobby probably has a reverse proxy like nginx or Caddy routing requests from the public URL to both ports. Let me just do a live test by checking what the server is actually doing.\n","thinkingSignature":"22f615318da2b12b7bf36a308435b54f2c2fd23ff17a7289d28f4a0d0b52f9b9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ltniaiptusie_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test if the Mission Control server has API proxy for /api -> localhost:3001\ncurl -s http://100.103.22.35:8787/api/music 2>&1 | head -3\necho \"---\"\ncurl -s http://100.103.22.35:8787/api/emails 2>&1 | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":441,"output":429,"cacheRead":77632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78502,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777787784598,"responseId":"064616882c9c219ad7555b2cf1f06b95"}}
