\":[{\"id\":\"2\",\"name\":\"Capitol One Quicksilver\",\"amount\":411,\"dueDate\":\"2026-03-27\",\"category\":\"Credit\",\"paid\":true,\"paidDate\":\"2026-03-27T17:30:14.499Z\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"name\":\"Chase\",\"amount\":74,\"dueDate\":\"2026-03-28\",\"category\":\"Credit\",\"paid\":true,\"paidDate\":\"2026-03-29T01:56:17.949Z\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"name\":\"Flex\",\"amount\":355.14,\"dueDate\":\"2026-03-31\",\"category\":\"Other\",\"paid\":true},{\"id\":\"5\",\"name\":\"Apple Card\",\"amount\":60,\"dueDate\":\"2026-03-31\",\"category\":\"Credit\",\"paid\":true,\"paidDate\":\"2026-03-29T01:56:19.081Z\"},{\"id\":\"tmobile-paid\",\"name\":\"T-Mobile\",\"amount\":98.29,\"dueDate\":\"2026-03-25\",\"category\":\"Phone\",\"paid\":true,\"paidDate\":\"2026-03-26T03:36:03.787Z\"},{\"id\":\"capone-4-15\",\"name\":\"Capitol One Quicksilver\",\"amount\":25,\"dueDate\":\"2026-04-15\",\"category\":\"Credit\",\"paid\":true,\"paidDate\":\"2026-04-15T00:00:00.000Z\"},{\"id\":\"discover-4-15\",\"name\":\"Discover\",\"amount\":25,\"dueDate\":\"2026-04-15\",\"category\":\"Credit\",\"paid\":true,\"paidDate\":\"2026-04-15T00:00:00.000Z\"},{\"id\":\"geico-4-15\",\"name\":\"GEICO\",\"amount\":187.25,\"dueDate\":\"2026-04-15\",\"category\":\"Insurance\",\"paid\":true,\"paidDate\":\"2026-04-15T00:00:00.000Z\"},{\"id\":\"capone-4-27\",\"name\":\"Capital One Quicksilver\",\"amount\":96,\"dueDate\":\"2026-04-27\",\"category\":\"Credit\",\"paid\":false}]}---\n{\"facts\":[{\"key\":\"bobby_name\",\"value\":\"scrolling\",\"from\":\"Cody\",\"ts\":1775680725199},{\"key\":\"bobby_name\",\"value\":\"looking\",\"from\":\"Cody\",\"ts\":1775681882573}],\"lastUpdated\":\"2026-04-08T20:58:03.912Z\"}","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-cody"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777787810002}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d92e403","parentId":"b985b4d7","timestamp":"2026-05-03T05:57:01.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - I can see the shared-memory has old entries about \"bobby_name\". That's what Bobby was doing earlier. I don't need to clean those up unless asked.\n\nNow let me look at the actual UI to understand what Bobby sees. The music widget is connected to Apple Music (Mac) and the email widget uses Gmail via gog. They both work - I confirmed this with my tests.\n\nBut Bobby says \"make sure everything is good.\" Maybe he's experienced issues or something specific isn't saving? Let me check the data directory and see if there are permission or lock issues.\n\nActually, I think I should just do a comprehensive test by posting some test data through all the save endpoints to confirm they work. Then clean up. But I already tested money/action and it works.\n \nLooking at the data more carefully - the bills widget shows Capitol One Quicksilver as marked paid in the history, but I'm seeing some inconsistency in what I'm reading. Let me test all the save endpoints systematically to verify they're actually working. Money saves properly through the API, habits work via POST, finnly has localStorage plus server sync, and bills support add, delete, and markPaid operations. I need to check music next.\n\nThe music widget uses osascript via a POST endpoint, so I should verify that actually works too. I'm also wondering if there's an input saving issue Bobby mentioned - looking at the money widget, the amount field only saves when you click the submit button, which is correct behavior, but maybe the UI isn't making it clear that saving happens on submission. Let me run through all these endpoints to confirm they're working.\n","thinkingSignature":"0f7243dcbf7375e7e5dfb019562b4417a8ad02981d61a3b4a7fed8011e575484"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nLet me do a full audit of all the data-saving endpoints:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ff9e8e0sky77_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test habits save\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3001/api/habits \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"habits\":[{\"date\":\"May 3, 2026\",\"water\":5,\"stretch\":2,\"laundry\":true,\"bedMade\":false,\"vacuum\":1,\"breakfast\":true,\"lunch\":false,\"dinner\":false}]}'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3301,"output":452,"cacheRead":82752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86505,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777787810005,"responseId":"064616a256a057728ff73fb0b8e7096c"}}
